DEPENDENCIES

  ocaml
  camlp4/ocaml-camlp4/ocaml-camlp4-devel
  flex
  bison
  indent
  ncurses-devel
  emacs

  for CELL
    you will also need the cell development package including ppu_intrinsics.h
    ,altivec.h etc in your include path (C_INCLUDE_PATH)
    (e.g. export C_INCLUDE_PATH=$C_INCLUDE_PATH:/opt/cell/toolchain/lib/gcc/ppu/4.1.1/include:/opt/cell/toolchain/lib/gcc/spu/4.1.1/include )
    and ppu32-gcc in your PATH
    (e.g. export PATH=$PATH:/opt/cell/toolchain/bin )


INSTALL

  ./configure && make
